      "name": "Sticky Note — Overview",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## WA_07_Save Setup State\n\n**Role:** Sub-workflow — dedicated write path for setup/onboarding data.\n\n**Action routing:**\n- `save_draft` → upsert to `setup_drafts` + update session stage\n- `commit` → upsert to `business_profiles` (full profile, persona, guardrails, hebrew_patterns) + update session\n- `none` → no DB write, returns success with saved=false\n\n**Tables used:**\n- `setup_drafts` — progressive draft storage keyed by session_id\n- `business_profiles` — final committed profile keyed by business_id\n- `sessions` — stage and setup_completed flag\n\n**Always returns:** `{ status, result: { saved, business_id, setup_completed }, error }`"
      }
    }
